\deqn{L = L_{fit} + \code{theory\_weight} \cdot L_{theory}}
where \eqn{L_{fit}} is the composite fit loss of \code{specification_search}
\deqn{L_{fit} = w_{rmsea}\max(0,(RMSEA-t_{rmsea})/0.03) +
